    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your knowledge of one particular combat sphere is without peer.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> 1 or more combat spheres.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Select one combat sphere you possess, you treat your base attack bonus as 1 higher for the purposes of its effects, but not for attacks made with talents from that sphere. At 5th level and every 4 levels afterwards, the chosen sphere&#8217;s base attack bonus is treated as an additional 1 higher, although the sphere&#8217;s effective base attack bonus cannot be higher than your character level.</p>\n<p><strong>Special:</strong> You may select this feat multiple times, each time selecting a different sphere.</p>\n",
